To have the ferret tools in this directory available in all ferret
scripts, add the following line to ~/.tcshrc (after installing ferret
via soft.init):

setenv FER_GO "$FER_GO $HOME/ferret/tools"

Alternatively, you can create a link to this directory and include the
tools directory in $FER_GO:

cd <my-ferret-files-dir>
ln -s $HOME/ferret/tools .
setenv FER_GO "$FER_GO ./tools"
